<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٦٢١ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ ,<span class="c5"> فِي قَوْلِهِ:</span> <span class="c3">{مُدْخَلَ صِدْقٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[الإسراء: ٨٠]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْمَدِينَةُ»</span> وَ <span class="c3">{مُخْرَجَ صَدْقٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[الإسراء: ٨٠]</span> ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَكَّةُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>